
# Architecture

This folder contains the solution architecture, system design, process flow diagrams, and agent orchestration diagrams for SDLC Foundry.

## High-Level Flow

Requirements (BRD/SOP/Transcript)
↓
Requirement Analyzer Agent
↓
PDD/SDD Generator Agent
↓
Human Approval
↓
Architecture Planner Agent
↓
Workflow Skeleton Builder Agent
↓
Human Enhancement
↓
Test Case Generator Agent
↓
Test Execution human in loop

## Components

- UiPath Maestro
- Agent Builder
- UiPath Apps
- Studio Web
- Test Cloud
- Coding Agents (Claude Code / Cursor)
- Human-in-the-Loop Approvals
